title: #520 - Felipe Esparza
description:
Felipe Esparza, comedian, co-host of the "What's Up Fool?" podcast, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.
 
Check out Felipe's new HBO special, "Translate This" on September 30th at 10pm.
